constellation.product.title: Constellation
constellation.product.description: Deploy ML models in your Workers applications
constellation.waitlist.description: Run machine learning models with Cloudflare Workers.
constellation.waitlist.example_desc: Run fast, low-latency inference tasks on pre-trained ML models natively on Cloudflare Worker scripts. Constellation supports some of the most popular ML/AI runtimes and multiple classes of models such as:
constellation.waitlist.example.item1: Image or audio classification or object detection
constellation.waitlist.example.item3: Text translation, summarization, or similarity analysis
constellation.waitlist.example.item6: Speech Recognition or Text to Speech
